        "- Data transformation\n",
        "- Feature importance\n",
        "- Feature selection\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## 19. Sonar Dataset\n",
        "\n",
        "The Sonar Dataset contains numerical attributes representing sonar signal measurements.\n",
