        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "# Conclusion\n",
        "\n",
        "Data preprocessing and feature engineering improve the quality and readiness of data before model training.\n",
        "\n",
        "Missing-value handling improves data completeness. Normalization and standardization bring numerical features to suitable scales. Data transformation improves feature distributions.\n",
        "\n",
        "Feature scaling ensures that numerical attributes contribute fairly to model calculations. Feature extraction using PCA transforms high-dimensional data into fewer principal components while preserving important information.\n",
        "\n",
